mouth of Death.

37:39.213 --> 37:41.259
"Timeless and lawless,

37:42.042 --> 37:44.697
"manifested as seven
spectral circles

37:44.740 --> 37:48.657
"spinning all that was,
is, and would be.

37:50.268 --> 37:53.009
"The Seven Circles be the
domain of the wandering dead,

37:53.053 --> 37:54.663
"and only the dead.

37:55.360 --> 37:57.623
"Their currency be truth,

37:57.666 --> 37:59.842
"but they traffic in trickery
for those

37:59.886 --> 38:02.236
"for whom death is not due.

38:03.063 --> 38:05.065
"If the string be cut,

38:05.108 --> 38:08.286
"the lost shall sleepeth
in the cradle of dark.

38:09.374 --> 38:12.290
"If the string be hoisted
back into the light,

38:12.333 --> 38:17.033
the lost shall be refound,
at the price of the string."

38:29.045 --> 38:31.657
[ominous music chimes]
♪♪

38:42.972 --> 38:44.191
[whispers]
Hangman,

38:44.234 --> 38:47.325
the card of ultimate
surrender.

38:47.977 --> 38:50.806
New perspective,
enlightenment.

39:04.994 --> 39:07.736
