42:15.750 --> 42:17.317
Lazy bum.

42:18.927 --> 42:20.581
[Kurt grunts]

42:53.614 --> 42:55.529
[saw whirring]

43:01.361 --> 43:03.450
[Kurt breathes heavily]

43:12.067 --> 43:13.852
[water splashes]

43:20.728 --> 43:22.687
[Echo whispers]
Tell her what you did.

43:24.514 --> 43:27.430
[exhales sharply]
[panting]

43:28.040 --> 43:29.607
[Echo whispers]
Tell her.

43:32.653 --> 43:34.612
[Echo whispers]
Tell her what you've done.

43:51.019 --> 43:52.804
[Echo whispers]
Tell her.

43:53.152 --> 43:55.110
[Echo whispers]
Tell her what you've done.

43:55.328 --> 43:57.286
[distant siren wailing]

43:57.330 --> 43:59.898
[unintelligible
phone conversation]

44:05.425 --> 44:07.166
- Twelve or thirteen...

44:10.256 --> 44:11.779
So, that's perfect.

44:14.869 --> 44:16.436
Yeah.

44:17.350 --> 44:18.699
All right,
I'm gonna go.

44:18.743 --> 44:20.527
All right, thank you.
Bye.

44:33.758 --> 44:34.802
Hungry?

44:35.368 --> 44:36.499
Drink?

44:36.935 --> 44:38.893
Water?
- No.

44:38.937 --> 44:40.373
- Sit.

44:43.898 --> 44:45.508
[Ivy sighs]

44:50.688 --> 44:52.080
- Nice place.

44:52.124 --> 44:53.691
- Thanks to you.

44:53.734 --> 44:55.518
You taught me
everything I know.

44:57.216 --> 44:58.826
- I lost my sight.

44:59.131 --> 45:00.915
- You lost your faith.

45:03.352 --> 45:04.789
- I read your book.

45:06.747 --> 45:08.749
Times bestseller list, huh?

45:10.664 --> 45:12.318
How much of it was true?

45:13.362 --> 45:14.712
- All of it.

45:17.279 --> 45:19.107
- In the book it says

45:19.151 --> 45:21.893
that you were given the key
to the Seven Circles.

45:22.807 --> 45:24.460
Is that true?

45:27.072 --> 45:29.378
Del, on the night
that Echo disappeared,

45:29.422 --> 45:31.685
she reached out to me
from the darkness.

45:31.729 --> 45:33.774
- That's a mother's intuition.

45:34.079 --> 45:35.471
- Maybe.

45:36.298 --> 45:38.257
[softly]
But then she revealed
to me a sign

45:38.300 --> 45:40.389
of the Seven Circles.

45:42.000 --> 45:45.177
And you know that has
nothing to do with intuition.

45:48.528 --> 45:50.095
Please.

45:57.798 --> 46:01.149
- The Seven Circles
are unforgiving.

46:03.804 --> 46:06.067
They are locked in grief.

46:07.503 --> 46:10.550
They will warp
everything within them.

46:12.117 --> 46:15.947
Every gift is its own
twisted curse.

46:18.688 --> 46:20.212
And for you,

46:20.255 --> 46:22.562
who's turned her back
on her calling,

46:22.605 --> 46:25.217
you will pay dearly.

46:26.218 --> 46:27.828
- I'll pay.

46:33.399 --> 46:35.967
[ominous music]
♪♪

46:43.496 --> 46:45.846
- Whoever opens the box

46:46.368 --> 46:49.067
enters the Seven Circles.

46:49.110 --> 46:52.070
But it is not you
who goes through them.

46:53.027 --> 46:55.464
It is they
that go through you.

47:03.385 --> 47:05.735
Once the door's opened,

47:05.779 --> 47:07.912
[whispers]
it cannot be shut.

47:13.613 --> 47:16.268
[eerie sounds whirring]

47:25.668 --> 47:27.279
[Ivy whispers]
- What happens now?

47:27.583 --> 47:29.890
[Del laughs maniacally]

47:54.175 --> 47:56.699
[electric guitar whirring]
♪♪

48:05.621 --> 48:08.537
[choking sounds]

48:21.507 --> 48:23.378
[gaging]

48:25.859 --> 48:27.817
[electric guitar whirring]
♪♪

48:29.558 --> 48:32.039
[gaging]

48:49.013 --> 48:51.493
[thunder rumbling]
[rain falling]

49:14.864 --> 49:16.127
- Listen,

49:16.170 --> 49:17.955
we just need to ask you
a couple more questions,

49:17.998 --> 49:19.695
we're still at square one.

49:21.349 --> 49:23.221
- Ivy,
did Echo ever talk about

49:23.264 --> 49:25.092
being bullied at school?

49:25.571 --> 49:27.094
[quietly]
- No.

49:30.315 --> 49:31.577
- You don't have any
reason to believe

49:31.620 --> 49:33.971
that she would have run away,
do you?

49:38.453 --> 49:40.412
- Echo did not run away.

49:41.195 --> 49:43.241
Something terrible
happened to her.

49:43.937 --> 49:46.809
I know, because
she reached out to me

49:46.853 --> 49:48.550
from another realm.

49:50.683 --> 49:53.816
I need you
to help me find out

49:54.556 --> 49:56.036
what happened to her.

49:56.080 --> 49:58.560
But you can't help me
find her.

49:59.431 --> 50:01.041
Only I can do that.

50:04.392 --> 50:05.524
Alone.

50:06.133 --> 50:07.221
- Okay.

50:07.265 --> 50:09.006
Ivy, one last thing.

50:12.226 --> 50:14.054
You said you left
Mrs. Minskey's

50:14.098 --> 50:15.708
at about nine that night?

50:15.751 --> 50:16.839
[echoing]
And the whole way home

50:16.883 --> 50:18.406
you didn't see
any other cars.

50:18.450 --> 50:19.929
Nobody passed you?

50:19.973 --> 50:21.322
[echoing]
- Okay, let's start
from the beginning.

50:21.366 --> 50:22.671
[echoing]
- You guys came home
after shopping.

50:22.715 --> 50:23.672
[echoing]
- What'd you get?
What you buy?

50:23.716 --> 50:24.760
Did Echo buy anything?

50:24.804 --> 50:25.979
[echoing]
- You made dinner,

50:26.023 --> 50:27.807
and then you left
at about seven, right?

50:27.850 --> 50:29.069
[echoing]
- Any boyfriend
or girlfriend

50:29.113 --> 50:30.592
in the picture
that you know of?

50:30.636 --> 50:32.159
[echoing]
- Does she disobey you often?

50:32.203 --> 50:34.031
[echoing]
- Do you think she
would hurt herself?

50:34.074 --> 50:36.033
[echoing]
- Do you happen to remember
your conversation with her?

50:37.512 --> 50:39.471
[banging]

50:42.822 --> 50:44.084
[drill whirring]

50:45.825 --> 50:48.306
[Kurt breathing heavily]

50:53.224 --> 50:55.095
- I know you're not real.

50:56.792 --> 50:59.056
- I'm as real
as I am dead.

51:01.971 --> 51:03.799
[Kurt sighs]

51:09.240 --> 51:11.329
[softly]
- I know you're not real.

51:15.072 --> 51:16.899
You're in my head.

51:17.161 --> 51:19.076
- I'm not in your head yet.

51:21.991 --> 51:23.384
Why don't you go get
your big gun

51:23.428 --> 51:25.560
and shoot me again?

51:26.779 --> 51:29.912
[Kurt inhales deeply]
[exhales]

51:29.956 --> 51:32.001
Tell my mother
what you've done.

51:45.014 --> 51:47.626
[radio playing rock music]
♪♪

