♪ Far away

52:07.298 --> 52:10.170
♪ I watch you drift
away from me

52:10.214 --> 52:12.520
♪ Far away

52:16.089 --> 52:18.744
♪ Far away

52:18.787 --> 52:21.921
[radio static]
♪ I watch you drift
