- For the past fifteen years,

52:30.277 --> 52:32.758
this is where we wind down
from a rough weekend

52:32.801 --> 52:34.542
and prepare
for another week.

52:34.586 --> 52:36.240
[low voice]
In hell.

52:36.283 --> 52:38.067
[laughs manically]

52:39.417 --> 52:40.766
We got some old,
